          <title>HIV infections could jump over 6 times if US support dropped &#38; not replaced, UNAIDS chief says</title>
          <description><![CDATA[The head of the U.N. AIDS agency said Monday the number of new HIV infections could jump more than six times by 2029 if American support of the biggest AIDS program is dropped, warning that millions of people could die and more resistant strains of the disease could emerge.]]></description>
